name: Nizuc Bek
Lore: 'Guard from Corulag. Former bouncer at the Mos Eisley cantina. Assigned by Jabba to guard celebrities visiting Jabba''s palace. Friend of Wuher. Loves juri juice.',
Text: 'Power +3 when present with your musician. When present at the start of a battle, may cause one character of ability < X to move away for free (or that character is immediately lost) where X = the number of your musicians present.',
